- Bottom nav: [lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart)
- Loading/Error states: [lib/widgets/common/loading_states.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/common/loading_states.dart), [lib/widgets/common/error_states.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/common/error_states.dart)
